de.feu.massim22.group3.map

Packages that use de.feu.massim22.group3.map
Package
Description
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.belief
Provides classes for storing the belief of an agent about the current simulation.
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.belief.reachable
Provides records for storing path finding information of a certain cell.
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.utilsV2
Provides utility classes and records for step processing of agents.
de.feu.massim22.group3.map
Provides classes for storing information of the agent environment and for navigation in this environment.
de.feu.massim22.group3.utils
Provides classes with helper methods and classes for debugging and logging.
de.feu.massim22.group3.utils.debugger
Provides classes of a debugging tool to visualize the agent environment, the current state of the simulation and also data of the decision process of the agents.
de.feu.massim22.group3.utils.debugger.debugData
Provides data classes to communicate between the main program and the debugger.
